ss=\"type-var\">'sint</span>)</span> <a href=\"../index.html#type-t\">t</a></span>, <span class=\"type-var\">'b</span>, <span class=\"type-var\">'c</span>)</span> <a href=\"argument-1-M/index.html#type-t\">M.t</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p><code>map_leaves f t</code> receives a mapping function <code>f</code> operating within the monad <code>M</code>, as well as a tree, and applys <code>f</code> to all <b>leaves</b> of the tree (not the inner nodes).</p></div></div>"}